data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION on this cozy two-bedroom, one bath home located on two city lots in East Carbon. Lot #22 Tax ID: 1C-0539-0000 is included in the sale. Possibility of a 3rd bedroom in the basement, room has a small window but no closet. Sit and relax in the large family room with newer carpet and tile flooring. Enjoy relaxing by the beautiful gas fireplace during the cooler evenings. Nice eat-in kitchen with newer cabinets, tile flooring, natural light and newer appliances. Large master bedroom with two large closets and newer carpet. Bathroom includes a walk-in tub/shower, tile floor and an updated vanity.  There are plenty of fruit trees on the property: Apricot, Apple and Cherry trees. One car garage detached from the house with cinder block walls and cement floor. There is plenty of room on the additional lot to park vehicles. Located close to the mountains, UTV/ATV trails, walking trails, Sunnyside Park, coke ovens near Columbia and the Sunnyside Rodeo Grounds. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from Carbon County Tax Records. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
